%h1
  Learning & development

%p
  %b
    Bridging the gap between mental wellness and performance training.
  
%p
  Businesses spend a lot of money on the minds of their staff. From management training to induction programmes, businesses invest in their people, so that their minds perform better. Our training programmes introduce valuable knowledge about the human mind into businesses, and our engagement services embed lasting cultural change and help you bring the best out of your people. We aim to go beyond statutory staff healthcare to use wellness as the foundation for peak organisational performance. 
  
%h2
  A Mind for Business
  
%p
  %i
    A Mind for Business
  is an education programme from Mindapples that teaches people to use their minds effectively. It offers bite-size insights from experimental psychology and neuroscience about how our minds work and how to use them, covering essential topics from handling pressure to thinking creatively. Each session is delivered by experienced trainers and packed with practical tools and techniques to increase your resilience, improve your mental performance, and manage yourself and others better. 
  
%p
  Our sessions are getting amazing feedback, with 
  %b
    over 90% of participants rating our sessions as "good" or "excellent" 
  and the same number saying they will change their behaviour as a result of what they have learnt. Here's what we offer:
  
%p
  These sessions are available as 60-minute masterclasses or 'lunch and learns' for up to 35 people, and 90-minute small-group sessions with additional discussion time for up to 12 people (perfect for team away days).

